<A>__{the clerk deposits the money, slams the register shut, and continues reading his yellow paper. confused, mariachi pockets his empty wallet and turns to find his room. the clerk peeks over his paper, eyeing the guitar case as mariachi goes. he hears the sound of mariachi's footsteps trailing off. the old man drops the paper and bolts silently to the phone as he dials el moco's phone number...}
